data.title: Kill Bill: Volume 2 (AKA Kill Bill Vol. 2)
data.meta_description: Kill Bill: Volume 2 (AKA Kill Bill Vol. 2) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. The document provides a detailed summary of the plot and characters of Kill Bill Vol. 2. After defeating two targets from her death list in the first film, The Bride continues pursuing the remaining targets (Budd and Elle Driver) before confronting her ultimate target, Bill. The summary describes the characters of Bill, Budd, and Elle Driver and their relationships with The Bride. It highlights a pivotal scene between The Bride and Bill and previews the climactic confrontation between The Bride and Elle Driver.
